學習規範 Course Policy
	    1.請勿缺課、遲到或早退。Don’t be absent, late or leave before the end of the class.
2.上課時請關手機。Please turn your cellular phone off.
3.鼓勵課堂發言與討論。Statement and discussion are welcome.
4.多閱讀劇本及相關書籍。Read drama (script) and related book as many as you can.
5.多觀賞戲劇演出或電影。Attend performance and go to movie as many as possible.      

