The Methdologies of Art: An Introduction ；Art History Bibliography8藝術史研究理論之範疇、方法、與基本概念；藝術史分期
Scope, methods and basic concepts9 藝術史學方法：形式、風格與類型、鑑識學、綜合分析學
Form, style and type；learning identification、Comprehensive analytics10圖像學、藝術文化社會學、藝術心理學、批判理論
Iconography、Sociology and Art/Culture、Psychology of Art、Critical Theory11文獻學：質化研究、文獻編纂與及寫作方法 
Bibliographie：Recherche qualitative、A literature review and research agenda、Writing research reports12問題討論：作品研究與查閱文獻演練、小論文大綱繳交
Seminar：Works of literature research and drills； Papers Outline due dates
(第十九周期末考周需繳交全文，並做十分鐘簡報。)
Full text will be required  on 19th week；ten min Oral presentations13論音樂藝術的本質About the Essence of Music14音樂學研究法則與基本訓練 Music Studies Rule and Basic Training15介紹四種主要的系統音樂學 Four Main Systems of the Musicology16解析音樂的體裁：音樂要素介紹 Music Texture: Introduction to the Various Elements of Music.17音樂句法的詮釋、各種樂曲類型 (歌曲、舞曲、頌樂等) 及其功能 Annotation of Music Structures; General Music, Song, Dance Music, Festival Music and its Function, etc.18報告繳交 Term paper due dates 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


